    IPatternMatcherContext

    public interface IPatternMatcherRuntimeContext
extends IPatternMatcherContext
    Represents all knowledge of the outside world, that is needed during runtime operation, towards the pattern matcher.

      • coalesceTraversals

        <V> V coalesceTraversals(java.util.concurrent.Callable<V> callable)
                  throws java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException
        The given runnable will be executed, and all model traversals will be delayed until the execution is done. If there are any outstanding information to be read from the model, a single coalesced model traversal will initialize the caches and deliver the notifications.
        Parameters:
        callable -
        Throws:
        java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException
